ORDER OF COURT
AND NOW, to-wit, this 22nd day of October, 1986, the Petition for Allowance of Appeal filed in the above-captioned case is GRANTED.
IT IS FURTHER ORDERED that said Petition is QUASHED. (See Opinion filed at 512 Pa. 217, 516 A.2d 647 (1986), Pennsylvania Dental Association, Appellant v. Commonwealth of Pennsylvania Insurance Department, et al.)
